    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sunny Trails tells the story of three Japanese goddesses who travel to an enchanted island in southern Brazil for a celebration of deities from around the world. But upon arriving on the island of Florianópolis, they find everything decorated and ready for the party, except for the guests. Countless stone statues rest on the beach… What could have happened?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/f62a4a1f8fa2232bb54b62aabbe8e474.poster.avif?t=1770385168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/f62a4a1f8fa2232bb54b62aabbe8e474.webm?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/f62a4a1f8fa2232bb54b62aabbe8e474.mp4?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ A wholesome world to explore</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventure to a paradise island in a world full of cute details and hidden surprises. In Sunny Trails, every corner of the island holds a story, a new friendship or a mystery to be unraveled. Perfect for those who love to relax while exploring magical worlds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Fish in crystal clear waters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Cook to improve stats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Try typical foods</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Collect magical items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Set up and decorate your own seaside camp</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/3add8b2e15348553c3e208debdf40b03.webp?t=1770385168\" width=14 height=15 /></span> Help eccentric and unforgettable characters<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/b15487ea286be3e8f4739e798a2f6151.poster.avif?t=1770385168\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/b15487ea286be3e8f4739e798a2f6151.webm?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/b15487ea286be3e8f4739e798a2f6151.mp4?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌞 Play as Amaterasu, the Goddess of the Sun, and lead this magical journey alongside her sisters, Susanoo and Tsukuyomi. Discover the secrets behind the mysterious visitor who enchanted the island and meet charming characters from Brazilian folklore and mythologies from around the world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/f7e926f4b5496603b9982b765d7c6288.avif?t=1770385168\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras_big/f7e926f4b5496603b9982b765d7c6288.avif?t=1770385168 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>⚔️ Strategic turn-based battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles in Sunny Trails are designed for those who enjoy gentle but deep challenges. Analyze each move calmly and face mythical creatures in stylish duels, special combos and surprising magical effects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/263d9702311b006b1633a128eec9e7bc.poster.avif?t=1770385168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/263d9702311b006b1633a128eec9e7bc.webm?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/263d9702311b006b1633a128eec9e7bc.mp4?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🗝️ A gripping mystery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even in a light and charming atmosphere, there is something dark lurking around the island of magic. As you investigate the uninvited visitor who turned the party guests into stone, you will immerse yourself in a plot full of magic, folklore and emotions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/8cc86e72dba2b8690b1104947ac68a12.poster.avif?t=1770385168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/8cc86e72dba2b8690b1104947ac68a12.webm?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/8cc86e72dba2b8690b1104947ac68a12.mp4?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>📕 Discover local literature</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sunny Trails is based on the fantastic tales of folklorist Franklin Cascaes, who dedicated his life to studying Azorean culture on Santa Catarina Island and the surrounding region. His work explores local legends and superstitions and provides a linguistic record of how this folklore was transmitted by the natives.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/2621565f7153ffbfae978903a4887457.poster.avif?t=1770385168\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/2621565f7153ffbfae978903a4887457.webm?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055290/extras/2621565f7153ffbfae978903a4887457.mp4?t=1770385168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
